@startuml
title Push New Message to Conversation Participants

actor Sender as "User (Sender)"
control Server as "Server"
collections Cache as "Server Cache\n(Conversation messages)"
control Client as "Recipient Client App"
boundary GUI as "Recipient GUI"

== Message received by server ==
Sender -> Server: Submit message for conversation
Server -> Cache: Add message to conversation cache

== Notify participants ==
Server -> Cache: Get all participants\nexcluding sender
Cache --> Server: Participant list

loop For each recipient
  Server -> Cache: Check recipient connection status\nand active conversation

  alt Recipient not connected
    Server -> Cache: Mark conversation as unread\nfor recipient
  else Recipient connected but viewing different conversation
    Server -> Cache: Mark conversation as unread\nfor recipient
    Server --> Client: Notify new message in conversation
    Client -> GUI: Show unread/new message indicator
  else Recipient connected and viewing this conversation
    Server --> Client: Deliver new message
    Client -> GUI: Display new message in conversation
  end
end
@enduml
